AVI Sees Full-Year Headline Earnings From Continuing Operations Rising 33%

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-06-22T13:24:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-22/avi-sees-full-year-headline-earnings-from-continuing-operations-rising-33-.html
AVI Ltd. (AVI)  said consolidated headline
earnings per share from continuing operations for the 12 months
to June 30 are expected to increase by between 23 percent and 33
percent from a year earlier.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
